    "In Stage-1, we pre-process the input publications to extract only highly relevant text.",
    "This task is challenging because genomic transcriptional regulations can differ between organisms, and molecular entities may behave differently under different cell conditions.",
    "We formulated a search criterion which ensured the extracted literature's association to the specified conditional parameters.",
    "Known attributes of the target network, such as the organism and cell function, were included to in narrow down the search to closely related literature.",
    "As published papers often include a keywords section that helps indexers, these were also used to establish relevance."
